.el .ds Aq '
.TH doctor 1  "doctor " 
.SH NAME
doctor \- Report runtime health and diagnostics for troubleshooting
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdoctor\fR [\fB\-\-format\fR] [\fB\-\-remote\fR] [\fB\-\-token\fR] [\fB\-\-timeout\-ms\fR] [\fB\-\-vscode\-manifest\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Report runtime health and diagnostics for troubleshooting
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-format\fR \fI<FORMAT>\fR [default: pretty]
Output format (pretty, json)
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
pretty
.IP \(bu 2
json
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-remote\fR \fI<REMOTE>\fR
Optional remote debug server to probe (e.g., localhost:9229)
.TP
\fB\-\-token\fR \fI<TOKEN>\fR
Authentication token for remote probe (if required by server)
.TP
\fB\-\-timeout\-ms\fR \fI<TIMEOUT_MS>\fR [default: 3000]
Timeout for remote checks in milliseconds
.TP
\fB\-\-vscode\-manifest\fR \fI<FILE>\fR
Optional path to a VS Code extension `package.json` to report version hints
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
